  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 13.34,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.34,
      "end": 34.33,
      "text": "자막 없이 영화를 볼 수 있는 그날까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.33,
      "end": 36.07,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.07,
      "end": 38.25,
      "text": "10월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.25,
      "end": 40.75,
      "text": "아 remake of the 2006 film"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.75,
      "end": 43.19,
      "text": "of the same name by Susan Biel"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.19,
      "end": 44.63,
      "text": "After the wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.63,
      "end": 47.15,
      "text": "After wedding in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.15,
      "end": 48.17,
      "text": "되겠습니다. 그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.43,
      "end": 50.75,
      "text": "Yes. After the wedding in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.75,
      "end": 53.13,
      "text": "the movie is mostly set in New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.13,
      "end": 55.25,
      "text": "맞아요. 대부분"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.25,
      "end": 58.71,
      "text": "New York에서 펼쳐지는 이야기가 들려질 텐데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.71,
      "end": 61.67,
      "text": "Anyway, so there is an original film"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.67,
      "end": 62.69,
      "text": "of this movie, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.89,
      "end": 65.51,
      "text": "Yes. Actually this movie is a remake"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.51,
      "end": 67.91,
      "text": "of a Danish-Swedish movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.91,
      "end": 70.27,
      "text": "that was made back in 2006"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.27,
      "end": 72.93,
      "text": "and I remember in college"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.93,
      "end": 75.01,
      "text": "I watched this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.01,
      "end": 78.05,
      "text": "and it impressed me so much"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.05,
      "end": 80.11,
      "text": "I watched the original movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.11,
      "end": 80.51,
      "text": "Wow!"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.07,
      "end": 81.39,
      "text": "완전"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.39,
      "end": 83.01,
      "text": "네, 너무 부러워요"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.01,
      "end": 83.65,
      "text": "Oh really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.77,
      "end": 84.03,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.03,
      "end": 84.67,
      "text": "Have you seen it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 84.79,
      "end": 85.15,
      "text": "아니요"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.15,
      "end": 87.03,
      "text": "I highly recommend it"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.03,
      "end": 88.35,
      "text": "After you see this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.35,
      "end": 89.79,
      "text": "you can watch the original"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.79,
      "end": 91.83,
      "text": "It was really good"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.83,
      "end": 93.57,
      "text": "Oh, was it really, really good?"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.81,
      "end": 94.17,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.17,
      "end": 96.57,
      "text": "It was basically the same story"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.57,
      "end": 98.31,
      "text": "except the main character"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.31,
      "end": 100.49,
      "text": "the manager of the orphanage"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.49,
      "end": 101.57,
      "text": "is a man"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.57,
      "end": 104.01,
      "text": "and he's called to Denmark"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.01,
      "end": 105.59,
      "text": "So in this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.59,
      "end": 106.25,
      "text": "she's a woman"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.25,
      "end": 107.19,
      "text": "she goes to New York"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.19,
      "end": 108.07,
      "text": "to get money"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.07,
      "end": 109.17,
      "text": "In this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.17,
      "end": 110.73,
      "text": "he is in India"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.73,
      "end": 111.51,
      "text": "and goes to Denmark"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.51,
      "end": 112.61,
      "text": "to get money"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.61,
      "end": 114.39,
      "text": "and then lots of twists"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.39,
      "end": 115.51,
      "text": "and turns happen"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.51,
      "end": 116.91,
      "text": "including a wedding"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.91,
      "end": 117.71,
      "text": "Very interesting"
    },
    {
      "start": 117.71,
      "end": 119.67,
      "text": "그러니까 원작에서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.67,
      "end": 121.29,
      "text": "덴마크에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.29,
      "end": 122.11,
      "text": "아니 그러니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.11,
      "end": 122.89,
      "text": "인디아에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.89,
      "end": 124.87,
      "text": "덴마크로 불려가는 상황이고"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.87,
      "end": 126.71,
      "text": "지금 우리가 보는 영화에서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.71,
      "end": 127.75,
      "text": "인디아에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.75,
      "end": 130.35,
      "text": "뉴욕으로 불려가는 상황이라는 거고"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.35,
      "end": 131.71,
      "text": "또 아까 들으셨잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.71,
      "end": 132.75,
      "text": "men에서 지금"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.75,
      "end": 135.01,
      "text": "women으로 바뀐 상황입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.01,
      "end": 135.31,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 135.63,
      "end": 136.01,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.01,
      "end": 137.25,
      "text": "and the original"
    },
    {
      "start": 137.25,
      "end": 139.43,
      "text": "got a lot of good reviews actually"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.43,
      "end": 140.91,
      "text": "and was nominated for"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.91,
      "end": 141.91,
      "text": "an academy award"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.91,
      "end": 143.59,
      "text": "for the best foreign language film"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.59,
      "end": 144.17,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.17,
      "end": 146.27,
      "text": "진짜 우리 크리스 씨가"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.27,
      "end": 147.31,
      "text": "이 원작을"
    },
    {
      "start": 147.31,
      "end": 148.49,
      "text": "하이 스쿨 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.49,
      "end": 149.37,
      "text": "보셨다고 그랬죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.45,
      "end": 149.83,
      "text": "College"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.83,
      "end": 150.73,
      "text": "아, college 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.73,
      "end": 151.41,
      "text": "보셨군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 151.41,
      "end": 152.73,
      "text": "It came out in 2006"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.73,
      "end": 153.39,
      "text": "but I saw it"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.39,
      "end": 154.21,
      "text": "a few years later"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.21,
      "end": 154.63,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.63,
      "end": 156.35,
      "text": "In 2009 I think"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.35,
      "end": 157.01,
      "text": "I remember"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.01,
      "end": 157.81,
      "text": "I was in my room"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.81,
      "end": 159.09,
      "text": "nighttime board"
    },
    {
      "start": 159.09,
      "end": 160.33,
      "text": "I went on"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.33,
      "end": 161.13,
      "text": "a knit to"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.13,
      "end": 161.63,
      "text": "dingding"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.63,
      "end": 163.05,
      "text": "and I found this movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.05,
      "end": 164.41,
      "text": "It was recommended"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.41,
      "end": 165.27,
      "text": "by someone"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.27,
      "end": 166.19,
      "text": "I think"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.19,
      "end": 167.25,
      "text": "and it was really good"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.25,
      "end": 168.11,
      "text": "I'm so curious"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.11,
      "end": 169.55,
      "text": "about the original too"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.55,
      "end": 171.25,
      "text": "I recommend it"
    },
    {
      "start": 171.25,
      "end": 172.73,
      "text": "네, 이렇게 추천해 주시니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.73,
      "end": 173.77,
      "text": "진짜 원작도"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.77,
      "end": 174.95,
      "text": "보면 좋을 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.95,
      "end": 176.23,
      "text": "먼저 오늘 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.23,
      "end": 176.89,
      "text": "듣고 올게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.89,
      "end": 178.21,
      "text": "Do you have kids?"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.67,
      "end": 178.91,
      "text": "No"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.91,
      "end": 179.83,
      "text": "Partner?"
    },
    {
      "start": 180.45,
      "end": 181.17,
      "text": "No, my work"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.17,
      "end": 181.87,
      "text": "is all consuming"
    },
    {
      "start": 181.87,
      "end": 182.91,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.91,
      "end": 183.61,
      "text": "I get it"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.61,
      "end": 184.05,
      "text": "It's a lot"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.05,
      "end": 185.23,
      "text": "It's really a lot"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.23,
      "end": 185.89,
      "text": "to manage both"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.89,
      "end": 186.93,
      "text": "I just always wanted both"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.93,
      "end": 187.43,
      "text": "so I sort of"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.43,
      "end": 188.33,
      "text": "worked hard at it"
    },
    {
      "start": 188.33,
      "end": 190.29,
      "text": "I have twin boys too"
    },
    {
      "start": 190.29,
      "end": 191.41,
      "text": "I worked hard"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.41,
      "end": 191.99,
      "text": "to get them"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.99,
      "end": 192.73,
      "text": "believe me"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.73,
      "end": 194.8,
      "text": "So we do have a list"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.8,
      "end": 195.48,
      "text": "of priorities"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.48,
      "end": 196.52,
      "text": "if you're interested"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.52,
      "end": 197.38,
      "text": "in seeing that"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.38,
      "end": 200.2,
      "text": "Oh, so this is the part"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.2,
      "end": 201.1,
      "text": "that connects to"
    },
    {
      "start": 201.1,
      "end": 202.76,
      "text": "yesterday's conversation"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.76,
      "end": 203.68,
      "text": "between Teresa"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.68,
      "end": 204.36,
      "text": "and Isabel"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.36,
      "end": 204.58,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.78,
      "end": 205.42,
      "text": "They're continuing"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.42,
      "end": 206.32,
      "text": "their conversation"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.32,
      "end": 206.74,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.74,
      "end": 207.36,
      "text": "And it's getting"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.36,
      "end": 208.04,
      "text": "a little bit"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.04,
      "end": 208.72,
      "text": "personal"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.72,
      "end": 209.72,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.72,
      "end": 210.66,
      "text": "분명히"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.66,
      "end": 211.42,
      "text": "어제 대화"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.42,
      "end": 212.1,
      "text": "들으셨잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.1,
      "end": 213.04,
      "text": "인도에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 213.04,
      "end": 214.58,
      "text": "그 현실에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.58,
      "end": 216.12,
      "text": "설명을 들은"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.12,
      "end": 217.3,
      "text": "Teresa인데"
    },
    {
      "start": 217.3,
      "end": 219.54,
      "text": "지금 질문하는 내용이"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.54,
      "end": 220.1,
      "text": "Family"
    },
    {
      "start": 220.1,
      "end": 221.42,
      "text": "Weddings"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.42,
      "end": 222.04,
      "text": "Partner?"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.04,
      "end": 223.04,
      "text": "이런 거 물어보고"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.04,
      "end": 224.3,
      "text": "Love life"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.3,
      "end": 226.06,
      "text": "It's their first meeting"
    },
    {
      "start": 226.06,
      "end": 227.84,
      "text": "It's a business meeting"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.84,
      "end": 228.4,
      "text": "그러니까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.4,
      "end": 229.42,
      "text": "To get money"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.42,
      "end": 230.04,
      "text": "It's different"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.04,
      "end": 231.54,
      "text": "from what I expected"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.54,
      "end": 232.34,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.34,
      "end": 233.4,
      "text": "It's kind of like"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.4,
      "end": 234.58,
      "text": "너 밀새리야"
    },
    {
      "start": 234.58,
      "end": 235.58,
      "text": "너 뭐 결혼했냐"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.58,
      "end": 237.12,
      "text": "아이는 있어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.12,
      "end": 238.1,
      "text": "아이는"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.1,
      "end": 240.4,
      "text": "Business meeting이라고 하기에는"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.4,
      "end": 241.16,
      "text": "좀 굉장히"
    },
    {
      "start": 241.16,
      "end": 242.14,
      "text": "personal해지는"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.14,
      "end": 243.04,
      "text": "경향이 있습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.04,
      "end": 245.42,
      "text": "There must be a reason"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.42,
      "end": 246.18,
      "text": "behind this"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.18,
      "end": 246.54,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.54,
      "end": 247.78,
      "text": "여기까지 제가"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.78,
      "end": 249.18,
      "text": "장면을 보면서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 249.18,
      "end": 250.24,
      "text": "It was probably"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.24,
      "end": 251.4,
      "text": "because Teresa"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.4,
      "end": 252.54,
      "text": "had too much money"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.54,
      "end": 254.88,
      "text": "너무 돈이 많아서"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.88,
      "end": 256.72,
      "text": "약간 건성건성"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.72,
      "end": 257.96,
      "text": "이렇게 일을 하는 건가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.08,
      "end": 259.6,
      "text": "라고 생각이 들 때가 있었어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.6,
      "end": 261.0,
      "text": "아 좀 건방지게"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.0,
      "end": 262.58,
      "text": "I'm a rich lady"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.58,
      "end": 263.46,
      "text": "약간 있는 자의"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.46,
      "end": 264.58,
      "text": "여유를 부린달까"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.58,
      "end": 266.26,
      "text": "There are so many"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.26,
      "end": 266.98,
      "text": "organizations"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.98,
      "end": 268.32,
      "text": "I can donate to"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.32,
      "end": 270.0,
      "text": "Why should I donate to yours?"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.34,
      "end": 270.84,
      "text": "Tell me about"
    },
    {
