    },
    {
      "start": 529.86,
      "end": 533.15,
      "text": "I just always wanted both"
    },
    {
      "start": 533.15,
      "end": 535.31,
      "text": "So I sort of worked hard at it"
    },
    {
      "start": 535.31,
      "end": 537.27,
      "text": "I just always wanted both"
    },
    {
      "start": 537.27,
      "end": 540.89,
      "text": "저는 그 두 가지를 다 항상 원했어요"
