      "end": 706.27,
      "text": "from this one show"
    },
    {
      "start": 706.27,
      "end": 706.65,
      "text": "Amazing"
    },
    {
      "start": 706.65,
      "end": 708.01,
      "text": "And it was a lot of fun"
    },
    {
      "start": 708.01,
      "end": 709.43,
      "text": "There were a ton of 사자성어"
    },
    {
      "start": 709.43,
      "end": 711.57,
      "text": "that are from 삼국지"
    },
    {
      "start": 711.57,
      "end": 712.83,
      "text": "And I didn't know that"
    },
    {
      "start": 712.83,
      "end": 714.33,
      "text": "until I read the comic books"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.33,
      "end": 714.77,
      "text": "Really?"
